<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Posts on ⚝</title><link>/post/</link><description>Recent content in Posts on ⚝</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 10 Jul 2021 19:42:58 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="/post/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>dirname和basename</title><link>/post/dirname%E5%92%8Cbasename/</link><pubDate>Sat, 10 Jul 2021 19:42:58 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/dirname%E5%92%8Cbasename/</guid><description>&lt;p>从路径获取目录部分或文件名部分可以分别使用&lt;code>dirname&lt;/code>和&lt;code>basename&lt;/code>命令。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Process Substitution 进程替换</title><link>/post/process-substitution-%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%E6%9B%BF%E6%8D%A2/</link><pubDate>Sat, 10 Jul 2021 14:39:29 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/process-substitution-%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%E6%9B%BF%E6%8D%A2/</guid><description>&lt;p>进程替换是一种重定向形式，其中进程的输入或输出（某些命令序列）作为临时文件出现。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Bash One Liners 3 重定向相关翻译与理解</title><link>/post/bash-one-liners-3-%E9%87%8D%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E7%BF%BB%E8%AF%91%E4%B8%8E%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3/</link><pubDate>Sat, 10 Jul 2021 14:25:39 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/bash-one-liners-3-%E9%87%8D%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E7%BF%BB%E8%AF%91%E4%B8%8E%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3/</guid><description>&lt;p>重定向其实是通过操作&lt;strong>文件描述符&lt;/strong>来完成的，这样会更容易理解。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>配置sftp</title><link>/post/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEsftp/</link><pubDate>Sun, 11 Apr 2021 16:49:23 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEsftp/</guid><description>&lt;p>sftp采用的是ssh加密隧道，安装性方面较ftp强，而且依赖的是系统自带的ssh服务，不像ftp还需要额外的进行安装&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Mysqldump</title><link>/post/mysqldump/</link><pubDate>Sun, 11 Apr 2021 16:38:46 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/mysqldump/</guid><description>&lt;p>mysqldump 是 MySQL 自带的逻辑备份工具。&lt;/p></description></item><item><t